    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Jacek Mańdziuk</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:164px;\"><a href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/d/d0/Jacek_mandziuk.jpg\" width=\"162\" height=\"208\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Jacek_mandziuk.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Jacek Mańdziu <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Jacek Mańdziuk</b>,<br />\na Polish computer scientist, mathematician, and full professor at Faculty of Mathematics and Information Science, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Warsaw_University_of_Technology\">Warsaw University of Technology</a> including multiple visiting positions, f.i. at  <a href=\"/University_of_Alberta\" title=\"University of Alberta\">University of Alberta</a> working with <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a> et al. . He holds a Ph. D. in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Applied_Mathematics\">Applied mathematics</a>, Faculty of Applied Physics and Mathematics, Institute of Mathematics, Warsaw University of Technology, 1993 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, and a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Habilitation\">Habilitation</a> in Computer science, Systems Research Institute, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Polish_Academy_of_Sciences\">Polish Academy of Sciences</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Warsaw\">Warsaw</a>, 2000. His research interests include the application of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computational_intelligence\">computational intelligence</a> (CI) methods to game playing, <a href=\"/Neural_Networks\" title=\"Neural Networks\">neural networks</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bioinformatics\">bioinformatics</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Financial_modeling\">financial modeling</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Time_series\">time series prediction</a> and development of constructive <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">learning</a> methods for <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intelligent_agent\">artificial agents</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1992_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1992 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jacek_Ma%C5%84dziuk&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1992_...\">1992 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jacek_Ma%C5%84dziuk&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1992 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/m/Macuk:Bohdan.html\">Bohdan Macukow</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i>A Neural Network designed to solve the N-Queens Problem</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/journals/bc/bc72.html#Mandziuk95\">Biological Cybernetics, Vol. 66 No. 4</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/PRACE/bc92.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/m/Macuk:Bohdan.html\">Bohdan Macukow</a> (<b>1993</b>). <i>A Neural Network performing Boolean Logic Operations</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.springerlink.com/content/1060-992x/\">Optical Memory and Neural Networks</a>, Vol. 2, No. 1, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/PRACE/omnn93.pdf\">pdf</a> </li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i>Solving the N-Queens Problem with a Binary Hopfield-type Network. Synchronous and asynchronous model</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/journals/bc/bc72.html#Mandziuk95\">Biological Cybernetics, Vol. 72, No. 5</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/PRACE/bc95.pdf\">pdf</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jacek_Ma%C5%84dziuk&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i>Neural Networks for the N-Queens Problem: a Review</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.scimagojr.com/journalsearch.php?q=12928&amp;tip=sid\">Control and Cybernetics</a>, Vol. 31, No. 2, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/PRACE/nqp-rev.pdf\">pdf</a> </li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Osman&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Daniel Osman (page does not exist)\">Daniel Osman</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i>Alpha-Beta Search Enhancements with a Real-Value Game-State Evaluation Function</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#27_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 27, No. 1</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/PRACE/ICGA.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Osman&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Daniel Osman (page does not exist)\">Daniel Osman</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i>Comparison of TDLeaf and TD learning in Game Playing Domain</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/iconip/iconip2004.html#OsmanM04\">11. ICONIP</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/PRACE/ICONIP04.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Osman&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Daniel Osman (page does not exist)\">Daniel Osman</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i>Temporal Difference Approach to Playing Give-Away Checkers</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/icaisc/icaisc2004.html#MandziukO04\">ICAISC 2004</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/PRACE/ICAISC04-3.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/k/Kusiak:Magdalena.html\">Magdalena Kusiak</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Karol_Wal%C4%99dzik&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Karol Walędzik (page does not exist)\">Karol Walędzik</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i>Evolution of Heuristics for Give-away Checkers</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/icann/icann2005-2.html#KusiakWM05\">15. ICANN</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/PRACE/ICANN05.pdf\">pdf</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Osman&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Daniel Osman (page does not exist)\">Daniel Osman</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i>TD-GAC: Machine Learning Experiment with Give-Away Checkers</i>. in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ipipan.eu/staff/m.draminski/\">M. Dramiński</a> et al. (Eds.) <i>Issues in Intelligent Systems. Models and Techniques</i>, 131-145, ISBN 83-87674-91-5, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/PRACE/td_gac_wisis.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/k/Kusiak:Magdalena.html\">Magdalena Kusiak</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Karol_Wal%C4%99dzik&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Karol Walędzik (page does not exist)\">Karol Walędzik</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (<b>2007</b>). <i>Evolutionary Approach to the Game of Checkers</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/icannga/icannga2007-1.html#KusiakWM07\">8. ICANNGA</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/PRACE/ICANNGA07-1.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=W%C5%82odzis%C5%82aw_Duch&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Włodzisław Duch (page does not exist)\">Włodzisław Duch</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (eds.) (<b>2007</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/book/10.1007%2F978-3-540-71984-7\">Challenges for Computational Intelligence</a></i>. Studies in Computational Intelligence, Vol. 63, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (<b>2007</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-71984-7_15\">Computational Intelligence in Mind Games</a></i>.</dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jacek_Ma%C5%84dziuk&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/book/10.1007%2F978-3-642-11678-0\">Knowledge-Free and Learning-Based Methods in Intelligent Game Playing</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/bookseries/7092\">Studies in Computational Intelligence</a>, Vol. 276, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Karol_Wal%C4%99dzik&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Karol Walędzik (page does not exist)\">Karol Walędzik</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>CI in General Game Playing - to date Achievements and Perspectives</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/icaisc/icaisc2010-2.html#WaledzikM10\">10. ICAISC</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/PRACE/ICAISC10.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Karol_Wal%C4%99dzik&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Karol Walędzik (page does not exist)\">Karol Walędzik</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>The Layered Learning method and its Application to Generation of Evaluation Functions for the Game of Checkers</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/ppsn/ppsn2010-2.html#WaledzikM10\">11. PPSN</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/PRACE/PPSN10.pdf\">pdf</a> </li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i>Towards Cognitively Plausible Game Playing Systems</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/journals/cim/cim6.html#Mandziuk11\">IEEE Computational Intelligence Magazine, Vol. 6, No. 2</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/PRACE/IEEE_CIM_draft.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Maciej_%C5%9Awiechowski&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Maciej Świechowski (page does not exist)\">Maciej Świechowski</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i>Generic Heuristic Approach to General Game Playing</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/sofsem/sofsem2012.html#MandziukS12\">38. SOFSEM</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/PRACE/SOFSEM12.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Karol_Wal%C4%99dzik&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Karol Walędzik (page does not exist)\">Karol Walędzik</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/265555737_An_Automatically_Generated_Evaluation_Function_in_General_Game_Playing\">An Automatically Generated Evaluation Function in General Game Playing</a></i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TOCIAIGAMES\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Computational Intelligence and AI in Games</a>, Vol. 6, No. 3</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Maciej_%C5%9Awiechowski&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Maciej Świechowski (page does not exist)\">Maciej Świechowski</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i>Self-Adaptation of Playing Strategies in General Game Playing</i>.  <a href=\"/IEEE#TOCIAIGAMES\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Computational Intelligence and AI in Games</a>, Vol. 6, No. 4</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Maciej_%C5%9Awiechowski&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Maciej Świechowski (page does not exist)\">Maciej Świechowski</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (<b>2016</b>). <i>A Hybrid Approach to Parallelization of Monte Carlo Tree Search in General Game Playing</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.springer.com/de/book/9783319301648\">Challenging Problems and Solutions in Intelligent Systems</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i>MCTS/UCT in Solving Real-Life Problems</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.springer.com/us/book/9783319679457\">Advances in Data Analysis with Computational Intelligence Methods</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Karol_Wal%C4%99dzik&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Karol Walędzik (page does not exist)\">Karol Walędzik</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jacek Mańdziuk</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i>Applying Hybrid Monte Carlo Tree Search Methods to Risk-Aware Project Scheduling Problem</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Information_Sciences_(journal)\">Information Sciences</a>, Vol. 460</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jacek_Ma%C5%84dziuk&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/\">Prof. Jacek Mańdziuk</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://lifeboat.com/ex/bios.jacek.mandziuk\">Lifeboat Foundation Bios: Professor Jacek Mańdziuk</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=KHxnO24AAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Jacek Mańdziuk - Google Scholar Citations</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jacek_Ma%C5%84dziuk&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/\">Prof. Jacek Mańdziuk</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/#page_content-02_biography\">Prof. Jacek Mańdziuk    | Biography</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mini.pw.edu.pl/~mandziuk/#page_content-05_publications\">Prof. Jacek Mańdziuk | Publications</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/m/Mandziuk:Jacek.html\">DBLP: Jacek Mandziuk</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\